ThreeFlaneurs Documentation

This document contains various components we have developed using ftd language.

Navbar Component

We have developed the navbar component for ThreeFlaneurs website.
Input
null
-- ftd.column:
if: { ftd.device == "desktop" }
width: fill-container
height.fixed.px: 61
background.solid: #fff

-- lib.navbar-desktop:
-- end: ftd.column

-- ftd.column:
if: { ftd.device == "mobile" }
width: fill-container

-- lib.navbar-mobile:

-- lib.navbar-dropdown:

-- end: ftd.column

-- ftd.column:
if: { ftd.device == "desktop" }
width: fill-container
height.fixed.px: 61
background.solid: #fff

-- lib.navbar-desktop:
-- end: ftd.column

-- ftd.column:
if: { ftd.device == "mobile" }
width: fill-container

-- lib.navbar-mobile:

-- lib.navbar-dropdown:

-- end: ftd.column

WHAT WE DO
WHO WE ARE
LATEST NEWS
3F JOURNAL
PUBLICATIONS

A multi-funcitonal blog component

We have developed a blog component for ThreeFlaneurs website.
Input
null
-- home.blog-1: WHAT WE DO .....
color: #f1562a
heading-margin: 100
content-1: We have hosted (open house format) public design events in several cities across UAE & India under our **Architecture Open** initiatives.
content-2: And also conducted **Curated Design Tours** to various cities around the world so as to foster a better understanding of the state of architecture and design in our contemporary cities.
button: Learn More
url: /what-we-do

-- home.blog-1: WHAT WE DO .....
color: #f1562a
heading-margin: 100
content-1: We have hosted (open house format) public design events in several cities across UAE & India under our **Architecture Open** initiatives.
content-2: And also conducted **Curated Design Tours** to various cities around the world so as to foster a better understanding of the state of architecture and design in our contemporary cities.
button: Learn More
url: /what-we-do
Output
WHAT WE DO …..
We have hosted (open house format) public design events in several cities across UAE & India under our Architecture Open initiatives.
And also conducted Curated Design Tours to various cities around the world so as to foster a better understanding of the state of architecture and design in our contemporary cities.
Learn More
